Package org.toolboxframework.scan.annotation

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Tool
    The Tool annotation is used to mark classes for inclusion in tool scanning.
    ToolMaker
    The ToolMaker annotation is used to mark classes that contain methods annotated with the Tool annotation for inclusion in tool scanning.
